      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_ECAFEA10-0993-0135-334F-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>As an account admin, you can <a href="/t5/Admin-Guide/How-do-I-customize-the-Canvas-Help-Menu-for-an-account/ta-p/127" target="_blank">customize the Help menu</a> that appears in Canvas for all users. You can also add custom help links for your institution and have them display to all or specific user roles.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
